{"tid":1233703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夠啦，唔好再互屌","createTime":"2019-06-16T20:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T04:29:08.000Z","uid":258197,"like":423,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"f69556ed55368b87e3d054f90be5e0c88e52e324","tid":1233703,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:34:52.000Z","msg":"平心靜氣啲先，唔理你邊一邊，大家唔係對立既好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直接講<br />\n和理非：<br />\n&mdash;唔好一黎就直接話人鬼（起碼，當人地係左做啲野時你問佢點解咁做但佢都解釋唔到先再算），搞清楚／fact check左先<br />\n&mdash;唔好隨便直接篤灰，唔該，好影響士氣<br />\n<br />\n勇武：<br />\n&mdash;知道最佳時機係幾時　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地無左和理非／勇武是旦一邊都唔掂，唔該唔好自亂陣腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW，乜Ｌ野５：０呀，未完場就係未完場。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係無階段性勝利，唔係最後完全勝利都仲係輸緊架</span></strong><br />\n都係個個比喻︰你份Assignment滿分無用，Final Grade都可以係爛／Fail <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想見到因為鬼論而分化，咁就算對家唔放鬼自己都玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4d821e15520c642f92a29e8e95e890ce92c530","tid":1233703,"uid":22632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f69556ed55368b87e3d054f90be5e0c88e52e324","tid":1233703,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:34:52.000Z","msg":"平心靜氣啲先，唔理你邊一邊，大家唔係對立既好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直接講<br />\n和理非：<br />\n&mdash;唔好一黎就直接話人鬼（起碼，當人地係左做啲野時你問佢點解咁做但佢都解釋唔到先再算），搞清楚／fact check左先<br />\n&mdash;唔好隨便直接篤灰，唔該，好影響士氣<br />\n<br />\n勇武：<br />\n&mdash;知道最佳時機係幾時　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地無左和理非／勇武是旦一邊都唔掂，唔該唔好自亂陣腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac